            <description><![CDATA[<h2>Meeting Coach 0.4.1</h2>
<ul>
  <li>Fixed: downloading a model on first launch no longer fails with "Could not connect to the server"</li>
  <li>Fixed: the recommended gemma4 models can now actually be downloaded (updated built-in AI engine)</li>
  <li>Download problems now show a clear error message instead of silently doing nothing</li>
  <li>The app no longer leaves its AI engine running after you quit</li>
</ul>
]]></description>
